install using:

$ bash < <(curl -s https://raw.github.com/jmervine/vim-config/master/install.sh)

To install :ConqueTerm --
$ cd 
$ vi .vim/src/conque_2.3.vmb

In vi run...

:so %
:q

... then reopen vi.

My ConqueTerm shortcuts are:
1. <leader>sh -- opens bash in a 10 row high window at the bottom of vi.
2. <leader>sr -- opens irb in the above window.
3. <leader>ss -- opens bash in the current buffer.
4. <leader>ssr -- opens irb in the current buffer.

